293
00:25:42,799 --> 00:25:44,480
Zhou Song and I have so many ideas,

294
00:25:45,359 --> 00:25:46,839
but none of them are useful.

295
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:35,759
Skin patch

296
00:26:41,279 --> 00:26:42,359
Painkillers

297
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,359
Elastic bandage

298
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,720
What else are you trying to teach me?

299
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,599
You won't call me until the competition starts.

300
00:26:58,960 --> 00:26:59,920
What's your attitude?

301
00:27:00,079 --> 00:27:02,359
Your elbow injury is common knowledge, and yet...

302
00:27:02,599 --> 00:27:03,759
...you still have the nerve to yell at me?

303
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:07,160
I know you don't want others to know about my old injury.

304
00:27:08,759 --> 00:27:10,039
There's no need to emphasize it every time.

305
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,039
The injury is your own fault.

306
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,599
Why are you competing with me?

307
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,640
The injury is your own fault.

308
00:27:16,119 --> 00:27:17,839
And yet you're the one feeling wronged.

309
00:27:23,519 --> 00:27:25,200
You really haven't changed at all.

310
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,880
Stop being so sarcastic.

311
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:27,839
I have only one thing to say.

312
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,319
No matter how much it hurts,

313
00:27:29,519 --> 00:27:31,559
you all have to stand firm on the court.

314
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:37,200
You're really something else as a mother.

315
00:27:37,759 --> 00:27:38,559
What did you say?

316
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,799
I said, of course I will.

317
00:27:49,559 --> 00:27:50,799
Even if it hurts like hell,

318
00:27:52,799 --> 00:27:54,240
I will stand on the court.

319
00:28:25,839 --> 00:28:27,920
I only went to him because I was really uncomfortable.

320
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,200
I didn't want to disturb your sleep.

321
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,440
Actually, if you had called,

322
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,079
I would have come over.

323
00:29:45,799 --> 00:29:48,079
To play well on the field,

324
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:52,319
you need to at least ensure your body is healthy.

325
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:58,880
I'll be in the living room.

326
00:29:59,759 --> 00:30:00,960
If you feel unwell,

327
00:30:01,279 --> 00:30:02,279
just call me anytime.

328
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:41,880
We meet again.

329
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,279
Teacher Li

330
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:54,160
He said he's Xiao Si's friend.

331
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,880
I didn't know who he was then.

332
00:32:01,839 --> 00:32:03,319
Don't try to get too close.

333
00:32:13,559 --> 00:32:15,039
You all saw that kid.

334
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:17,119
He seemed so clueless.

335
00:32:17,799 --> 00:32:18,960
Don't let your guard down.

336
00:32:19,279 --> 00:32:20,480
Think about what we researched.

337
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,759
A comprehensive tactical response.

338
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:23,359
Those focused on team play, think team play.

339
00:32:23,559 --> 00:32:24,680
Those focused on individual play, think individual play.

340
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,799
Okay.

341
00:32:28,079 --> 00:32:28,519
Coach.

342
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:30,720
His hand injury should hold up for this match.

343
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:31,160
Alright.

344
00:32:32,279 --> 00:32:32,920
Okay, give it to me.

345
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,359
Li Youen

346
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,599
I really didn't expect this.

347
00:32:45,039 --> 00:32:47,000
So you're Zhai Qiuyu's

348
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,359
team doctor?

349
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,039
I didn't expect that either.

350
00:32:52,119 --> 00:32:53,720
A team doctor can switch to being an athlete.

351
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:57,759
Don't rush off.

352
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:08,240
Everyone's so busy.

353
00:33:08,839 --> 00:33:10,640
You still have time to chat with an old acquaintance.

354
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,279
Get back to work.

355
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:21,279
I don't care what your intentions are,

356
00:33:21,759 --> 00:33:22,920
but I'm warning you,

357
00:33:23,759 --> 00:33:25,119
stay away from my people.

358
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:33,359
They really are your people.

359
00:33:55,279 --> 00:33:56,160
Let me help you.

360
00:33:58,079 --> 00:33:59,079
Don't bother me here.

361
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:01,480
We haven't settled the score from earlier.

362
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:05,920
Gu Hao,

363
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:07,759
take him to the lounge.

364
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,480
No need.

365
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:12,800
I'll walk myself.

366
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:28,239
Zhai Qiuyu wins the second round.

367
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:31,239
Zhai Qiuyu and Chen Mo are now tied.

368
00:34:31,559 --> 00:34:32,400
That's great!

369
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:34,559
Teacher Li,

370
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,360
Qiuyu's right elbow is acting up again.

371
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,679
Can you come quickly and help him?

372
00:34:38,239 --> 00:34:39,039
What's wrong?

373
00:34:39,239 --> 00:34:40,320
Didn't you win the second round?

374
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:41,320
We fell into their trap.

375
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,239
Chen Mo kept forcing Qiuyu to use his backhand.

376
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,559
He can't hold on much longer.

377
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,039
Teacher Li, slow down.

378
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,639
Just bear with it.

379
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:08,159
You

380
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:27,599
That's good.

381
00:35:31,679 --> 00:35:31,920
Okay.

382
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:33,559
Go, go, Brother Yu!

383
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:37,480
Come on, come on!

384
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,119
Are you okay?

385
00:35:48,559 --> 00:35:49,119
I'm fine.

386
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,480
I'll head back to the lounge first.

387
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,559
Zhai Qiuyu has now reached match point.

388
00:35:54,559 --> 00:35:56,000
He just needs to win one more point

389
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:58,159
to win this match.

390
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,440
What a shame.

391
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,920
If Chen Mo wins one more point,

392
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,039
the score will be tied again.

393
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:06,800
Is there something wrong with Zhai Qiuyu's racket?

394
00:36:07,519 --> 00:36:09,440
Zhai Qiuyu has called a timeout to change his racket.

395
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:13,159
Hello?

396
00:36:13,199 --> 00:36:13,719
Gu Hao

397
00:36:13,719 --> 00:36:14,320
What's up?

398
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:14,960
Teacher Li

399
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,159
Qiu Yu's string broke.

400
00:36:16,199 --> 00:36:17,480
Quick, get his spare racket.

401
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,360
I'm coming right now.

402
00:36:27,159 --> 00:36:27,920
Where's the racket?

403
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:42,719
Go, go, go, Yu Ge!

404
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:45,719
Teacher Li

405
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,320
You shouldn't go back.

406
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:49,800
Please, have a seat.

407
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,719
What a terrible racket.

408
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:04,000
It's not worn out.

409
00:38:05,039 --> 00:38:06,360
Someone tampered with it.

410
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,920
Why would the spare racket have this problem?

411
00:38:16,039 --> 00:38:17,519
I took it out to check before the match.

412
00:38:17,519 --> 00:38:18,440
It was fine.

413
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,400
And I had Coach Wang check it too.

414
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,000
Right.

415
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,679
I definitely checked it.

416
00:38:22,679 --> 00:38:23,960
How could this happen?

417
00:38:24,199 --> 00:38:25,320
Who did this?

418
00:38:25,519 --> 00:38:27,000
The spare racket was in the lounge.

419
00:38:27,159 --> 00:38:28,559
It was Li Youen who brought it onto the court.

420
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:31,159
The spare racket might have been in the lounge

421
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,719
and deliberately damaged.

422
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,000
It wasn't necessarily Teacher Li.

423
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,039
Who else went into the lounge?

424
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:38,280
No one else.

425
00:38:38,719 --> 00:38:40,559
Then it must have been you in the lounge.

426
00:38:41,159 --> 00:38:41,639
Me?

427
00:38:42,199 --> 00:38:42,960
It wasn't me.

428
00:38:47,719 --> 00:38:48,519
Zhai Qiuyu

429
00:38:49,559 --> 00:38:50,519
It really wasn't me.

430
00:38:50,519 --> 00:38:52,119
You'd better explain.

431
00:38:52,119 --> 00:38:54,599
Why was the initial injury report handled by you

432
00:38:54,719 --> 00:38:55,800
and then leaked to the media?

433
00:38:56,199 --> 00:38:57,320
Now the racket is the same.

434
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,320
Everything

435
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,840
happened after you joined the club.

436
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:02,960
Li Youen,

437
00:39:03,519 --> 00:39:04,679
I can't cover for you anymore.

438
00:39:05,239 --> 00:39:06,400
You'd better explain it all clearly.

439
00:39:06,719 --> 00:39:07,199
And

440
00:39:07,519 --> 00:39:08,840
it seems you've known Chen Mo for a long time.

441
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,920
I even greeted him before the match.

442
00:39:11,199 --> 00:39:12,679
Now I have to doubt

443
00:39:13,199 --> 00:39:14,239
if Chen Mo bribed you.

444
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,920
I have indeed met Chen Mo,

445
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:17,719
but

446
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:18,840
but I really didn't...

447
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,360
How much money did Chen Mo give you?

448
00:39:22,719 --> 00:39:23,880
Please believe me.

449
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:24,840
I didn't.

450
00:39:25,639 --> 00:39:26,880
I don't want to see you again.

451
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:32,039
Qiu Yu, Brother Qiu Yu, Qiu Yu.
